This System was used for collecting tweets and submitting relevant tweets for Scenario A (push notifications) in TREC Real-Time Summarization Track 2016. The system had successfully collected more than 50 GB tweets, submitted 4142 relevant tweets based on 203 topics over 10 days of span. 
 

More info on TREC:- http://trec.nist.gov/
More info on RTS Track:-	http://trecrts.github.io/ 
More info on Tweet API:- https://apps.twitter.com/

Note:	To run the system get your own twitter api subscription and use access and subscription token from twitter. Contact the undersigned for further information.

